	<item>
		<title>CBK to Regulate Digital Lenders: The Central Bank of Kenya (Amendment) Act, 2021 Passed Into Law</title>
		<link>https://www.oraro.co.ke/cbk-to-regulate-digital-lenders/</link>
					<comments>https://www.oraro.co.ke/cbk-to-regulate-digital-lenders/#respond</comments>
		
