		<title>Scaling Up: The Potential of Kenya’s Proposed Renewable Energy Auctions Policy</title>
		<link>https://www.oraro.co.ke/scaling-up-the-potential-of-kenyas-proposed-renewable-energy-auctions-policy/</link>
